summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the permit granted to Commercial Automotive Service, Inc. by Ordinance 92959 to construct, maintain and operate a tunnel under and across the alley in Block 89, D. T. Denny's 5th Addition to Seattle, by amending Section 8, repealing Sections 9 and 11 thereof, and adding new sections 9 and 11 to revise the amount of surety bond and liability insurance required, and to establish the annual fee for one year (July 1984 to June 1985).
